room_title: Escape room "Dracula's Crypt" by Bam! in Zeeland
room_description: Your team of fearless vampire hunters creeps into the forbidden resting place of the legendary Count Dracula. As you enter his dark domain, a secret lock traps you in. The hunters have become the hunted and the stakes are high! It's only one hour before sundown and we all know what that means. Find a stake cleverly hidden by your ancestors and drive it into Dracula's heart before he rises from the dead or you will become the next victims of this creature of the night.
